### 투표 API 테스트

### 변수 설정
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@roomId = 1
@voteId = 1
@optionId = 1

### ========================================
### 0. 방 생성
### ========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomName": "테스트 방",
  "targetBudget": 100000,
  "syncMode": "FOLLOW",
  "roomMeta": {
    "shoppingPurpose": "생일 선물 구매",
    "interestCategories": ["전자기기", "패션"],
    "headcount": 3,
    "budgetMin": 50000
  }
}

### ========================================
### 0-1. 방 조회
### ========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}

### ========================================
### 1. 투표 생성 (호스트 전용)
### ========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "점심 메뉴 투표",
  "options": ["짜장면", "짬뽕", "볶음밥"]
}

### ========================================
### 2. 투표 목록 조회 (전체)
### ========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes

### ========================================
### 3. 투표 목록 조회 (OPEN 상태만)
### ========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes?status=OPEN

### ========================================
### 4. 투표 목록 조회 (CLOSED 상태만)
### ========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes?status=CLOSED

### ========================================
### 5. 투표 상세 조회
### ========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes/{{voteId}}

### ========================================
### 6. 투표 참여
### ========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes/{{voteId}}/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "optionId": {{optionId}}
}

### ========================================
### 7. 투표 마감 (호스트 전용)
### ========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/{{roomId}}/votes/{{voteId}}/close
